                                 Employment

   The United States Bankruptcy Court for the Eastern District of
   Louisiana is an equal opportunity employer. The application form is
   available from the clerk's office. You also can download the
   Application for Judicial Branch Federal Employment Form in PDF format.
   Current job openings:
   Deputy Clerk
